Automation Basics (PyTest)
What is Automation Testing?

Before automation we were doing:

Manual check:

Check if model prediction is correct
Check if dataset has missing values
Check if API returns response

But companies automate these checks.

Example:

Instead of manually checking dataset every day, we write a test script.

The script runs automatically and tells:

✅ PASS
❌ FAIL

That is Automation QA.

